{"example_id":1326,"task":"operations.overdue_inspection_summary","prompt":[{"role":"system","content":"You are a workflow automation agent. Execute the requested tasks using the available tools. Do not ask clarifying questions - use the information provided and make reasonable assumptions when needed."},{"role":"user","content":"Can you pull together the overdue inspections report? Today is 2026-02-09. We need to check our field inspection records and see which sites have fallen behind schedule.\n\nEach site is on either a monthly or quarterly rotation. If a site's next inspection date has passed, it's overdue. Sites that are significantly overdue need an Asana task in the Facilities project (workspace ws_facilities, project proj_inspections, section sec_overdue) - our threshold for 'significantly' is more than two weeks past due.\n\nEmail the full list of overdue sites to the inspections coordinator. Include the last visit date and how far behind each site is. Only flag sites where inspections are still active - anything marked as suspended should be excluded."}],"answer":"","info":{"zapier_tools":["google_sheets_get_many_rows","asana_find_section","asana_create_task","asana_add_task_to_section","gmail_send_email","google_drive_find_multiple_files","google_sheets_get_spreadsheet_by_id","google_sheets_find_worksheet","asana_list_projects"],"initial_state":{"google_sheets":{"spreadsheets":[{"id":"ss_inspections","title":"Field Inspections","worksheets":[{"id":"ws_log","title":"Inspection Log","rows":[{"row_id":2,"cells":{"Site":"Westfield Distribution Center","Last Visit":"2025-12-10","Frequency":"Monthly","Inspector":"K. Nguyen","Status":"Active","Notes":""}},{"row_id":3,"cells":{"Site":"Westfield Storage Annex","Last Visit":"2026-01-25","Frequency":"Monthly","Inspector":"K. Nguyen","Status":"Active","Notes":""}},{"row_id":4,"cells":{"Site":"Eastgate Manufacturing","Last Visit":"2025-10-15","Frequency":"Quarterly","Inspector":"M. Torres","Status":"Active","Notes":"